</header><article class="story story-blogpost"><a name="mainContent"></a><p class="category"><a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=127602855">America</a></p> <!--googleon: index--><div class="storytitle">
      <h1>'Fire Tracker': Online Tool To Monitor Blaze Near Yosemite</h1>
   <input type="hidden" id="title215697233" value="'Fire Tracker': Online Tool To Monitor Blaze Near Yosemite"></input>
   <input type="hidden" id="modelShortUrl215697233" value="http://n.pr/1fdFf8G"></input>
   <input type="hidden" id="modelFullUrl215697233" value="http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2013/08/26/215697233/fire-tracker-online-tool-to-monitor-blaze-near-yosemite"></input>
