                  <img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2013/08/26/fire262way-f6029a092f153c5587821399a1cdc9ce2ce72295-s6-c30.jpg" data-original="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2013/08/26/fire262way-f6029a092f153c5587821399a1cdc9ce2ce72295.jpg" class="img lazyOnLoad"  title="Some of the flames Saturday as the &quot;Rim Fire&quot; spread near Northern California's Yosemite National Park." alt="Some of the flames Saturday as the &quot;Rim Fire&quot; spread near Northern California's Yosemite National Park." />         <a href="#" class="enlargebtn" title="Enlarge">Enlarge image</a>         <a href="#" class="enlargebtn enlarge-smallscreen" title="Enlarge">i</a>
